1) jaguar_ARMA.cpp -- c++ code to compute the joint score test statistic and the corresponding p-value using RcppArmadillo template.

2) testJAG.R -- R script that can be run to test the above code. The R file runs power simulations.

3) jaguar.cpp -- c++ code to compute the joint score test statistic and the corresponding p-value following the closed-form solution using Rcpp template.

4) benchmark.R -- R script benchmarking two solutions a) RcppArmadillo, and b) Rcpp closed-form solution 

All .Rout files have executed R codes.